title: Bosch Refrigerator Water Filter
description: Bosch Refrigerator Water Filter ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 1 Review PartSelect Number PS16556076 Manufacturer Part Number 11034152 This genuine Bosch water filter is used to help reduce contaminants in the water supply including chlorine and lead. The water filter measures approximately 2 inches in diameter and is 9 inches long. It is recommended by the manufacturer to replace the water filter every 6 months for best performance.

installationInstructions.author: Louise from PLYMOUTH, MI
installationInstructions.title: Water filter needed replacement
installationInstructions.content: I mistakenly ordered the wrong part number online and the filter was too big.  I called Part Select and the gentleman knew the correct part number and sent it.  I also received directions for returning the incorrect part.
